SUMMARY:Deadline: We Are Human Festival 2026: Call for Films (Paris)
DESCRIPTION:Call for short films (1-10 minutes) involving human/AI hybrid c
 reation\, from the We Are Human Foundation in Paris. Three cash awards: Gr
 and Prix EUR 5\,000\, Best Screenplay EUR 3\,000\, and an Ethics Award EUR
  2\,000. ELIGIBILITY: international\, applicants 18+\; films must have bee
 n completed after 1 June 2025 and involve human/AI hybrid creation\; a man
 datory Ethics Notebook accompanies each submission. No submission fee. Fes
 tival screening at Forum des images\, Paris\, on 24 November 2026. Apply v
 ia FilmFreeway\; deadline 30 September 2026.\n\nOrganisation: We Are Human
  Foundation\nLocation: Paris\, France (Forum des images screening 24 Novem
 ber 2026)\nAward: Grand Prix EUR 5\,000\; Best Screenplay EUR 3\,000\; Eth
 ics Award EUR 2\,000. No submission fee.\nDuration: Annual short-film fest
 ival (screening 24 November 2026)\n\nMore: https://wearehuman.foundation/e
 n/call-for-films/?utm_source=artificialnouveaugrantdesk&utm_medium=referra
 l
URL:https://wearehuman.foundation/en/call-for-films/?utm_source=artificialn
 ouveaugrantdesk&utm_medium=referral
LOCATION:Paris\, France (Forum des images screening 24 November 2026)
END:VEVENT
