SUMMARY:Deadline: RIFF: Reykjavik International Film Festival 2026 Submissi
 ons
DESCRIPTION:The Reykjavik International Film Festival accepts shorts (under
  60 minutes) and features across all genres including documentary and hybr
 id work\, completed after 1 January 2025\, requiring at minimum an Iceland
  premiere. Late deadline 24 July 2026\; submission fee 7\,600 ISK (approx.
  EUR 60) via FilmFreeway.\n\nOrganisation: Reykjavik International Film Fe
 stival (RIFF)\nLocation: Reykjavik\, Iceland (festival 24 September to 4 O
 ctober 2026). Open to international entries\; minimum Iceland premiere.\nA
 ward: Screening at RIFF's 23rd edition. Submission fee 7\,600 ISK (approx.
  EUR 60).\nDuration: Festival 24 September to 4 October 2026. Films comple
 ted after 1 January 2025\; shorts under 60 minutes and features\, all genr
 es.\n\nMore: https://riff.is/en/?utm_source=artificialnouveaugrantdesk&utm
 _medium=referral
