DTSTAMP:20260713T104504Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260720
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260721
SUMMARY:Deadline: Mezipatra Queer Film Festival 2026 (27th edition) Submiss
 ions
DESCRIPTION:Mezipatra\, Central Europe's leading queer film festival\, scre
 ens in Prague and Brno each November. International queer-themed films can
  submit until 20 July 2026 (the free early-bird window ended 31 May\; a sm
 all fee now applies). Selected films are notified by 12 October 2026.\n\nO
 rganisation: Mezipatra\nLocation: Prague (5-12 November) and Brno (13-20 N
 ovember)\, Czech Republic. Open internationally.\nAward: Competition scree
 ning at Central Europe's main queer film festival. A small late-phase subm
 ission fee applies (free early bird ended 31 May).\nDuration: Festival Nov
 ember 2026\; selection notified by 12 October 2026.\n\nMore: https://www.m
 ezipatra.cz/en/?utm_source=artificialnouveaugrantdesk&utm_medium=referral
URL:https://www.mezipatra.cz/en/?utm_source=artificialnouveaugrantdesk&utm_
 medium=referral
LOCATION:Prague (5-12 November) and Brno (13-20 November)\, Czech Republic.
  Open internationally.
END:VEVENT
