 st 2026 via Festhome or FilmFreeway (platform fees vary).\n\nOrganisation:
  Fundacion Triangulo\nLocation: Madrid\, Spain (festival November 2026). O
 pen internationally.\nAward: Screening plus prizes up to EUR 2\,500 at a G
 oya- and Feroz-qualifying festival. Platform submission fees apply (Festho
 me/FilmFreeway).\nDuration: Festival November 2026\; notification by 2 Nov
 ember 2026.\n\nMore: https://www.lesgaicinemad.com/?utm_source=artificialn
 ouveaugrantdesk&utm_medium=referral
URL:https://www.lesgaicinemad.com/?utm_source=artificialnouveaugrantdesk&ut
 m_medium=referral
